Figure 4: Second inner loop of the model architecture which is iterating new particle launches over all grid elements with an individual and grid element area dependent weight. The orange highlighted path indicates the conversion of the exospheric species into other species, e.g. the photodissociation of water into atomic hydrogen and hydroxyl which has been carried over from the inner loop, see Figure 3.




